item.title: CVE-2016-10561|2024-08-06T03:30:19.095Z -- hackerone -- bitty%20node%20module
item.description: Bitty is a development web server tool that functions similar to `python -m SimpleHTTPServer`. Version 0.2.10 has a directory traversal vulnerability that is exploitable via the URL path in GET requests.
